OL,3,CNorth Wales hospital 'failed to care'
OL,4,Cfor an adult with learning disabilities
OL,6,FStaff at a hospital in north Wales
OL,7,Ffailed to care for an adult with
OL,8,Flearning disabilities, according to a
OL,9,Fnew report.
OL,11,FThe Welsh Ombudsman launched an
OL,12,Finvestigation after a woman, referred
OL,13,Fto in the report as Ms D, complained
OL,14,Fabout the care and treatment her
OL,15,Fsister, Ms A, received from Wrexham
OL,16,FMaelor Hospital in July 2022.
