OL,3,CNorth Wales hospital 'failed to care'
OL,4,Cfor an adult with learning disabilities
OL,6,FMs A had several medical conditions,
OL,7,Fincluding epilepsy, cerebral palsy and
OL,8,Flearning disabilities. She lived in a
OL,9,Fnursing home, had limited
OL,10,Fcommunication, and required 24 hour
OL,11,Fcare and support.
OL,13,FA Public Interest Report issued by the
OL,14,FOmbudsman found failings in nursing
OL,15,Fcare for Ms A, including failing to
OL,16,Fmonitor and manage Ms A's pain and
OL,17,Fepilepsy.
