OL,3,CNorth Wales hospital 'failed to care'
OL,4,Cfor an adult with learning disabilities
OL,6,F"And for the patient concerned, that
OL,7,Fwould have been very frightening and
OL,8,Fdistressing because her pain wasn't
OL,9,Fmanaged properly, her epilepsy wasn't
OL,10,Fmanaged properly and her very specific
OL,11,Fneeds weren't taken into account."
OL,13,FMs Morris added that the reason she
OL,14,Fhas published the public interest
OL,15,Freport is because there is some
OL,16,F"important learning to be taken from
OL,17,Fthis that is not only applicable to
OL,18,Fthis health board, to Betsi Cadwaladr,
OL,19,Fbut to all health boards in Wales who
OL,20,Foffer care to people with limited
OL,21,Fcapacity and disabilities."
