OL,3,CNorth Wales hospital 'failed to care'
OL,4,Cfor an adult with learning disabilities
OL,6,FDr Chris Stockport, Executive Director
OL,7,Fof Transformation and Strategic
OL,8,FPlanning for Betsi Cadwaladr
OL,9,FUniversity Health Board, said: "I
OL,10,Fsincerely apologise to Ms A and D, on
OL,11,Fbehalf of the Health Board, and we
OL,12,Fwill also writing a direct letter of
OL,13,Fapology for the failings in the care
OL,14,Fwe provided and how the complaint was
OL,15,Fhandled.
OL,17,F"Ms A's care fell below the standard
OL,18,Fwe expect, and we accept all of the
OL,19,FOmbudsman's recommendations.
